description: Forest Hybrid Jacket is designed for active hunting when you want to be both mobile and well protected from the weather and terrain. Made from wind- and water-resistant G-1000 Silent with underarm stretch gussets and Hydratic reinforcements over the shoulders for extra protection against getting wet. Clean design with simple, reliable features – e.g. warm hand pockets that will defrost cold hands quickly and top-loaded pockets lower down.
name: Fjallraven Forest Hybrid Jacket - Mens
